1
00:01:24,510 --> 00:01:30,220
[Mirror: A Tale of Twin Cities]

2
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:33,180
[Episode 6]

3
00:02:26,810 --> 00:02:30,320
[Cangliu - Hall of the Five Masters]

4
00:02:37,930 --> 00:02:40,160
[Yu Zhu - Cangliu Saintess]

5
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:43,420
The Greed Wolf Star is shifting abnormally thus chaos will surely arise.

6
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:47,140
Saintess, please tell me where is the Greed Wolf Star shifting abnormally?
 [Master Xian - One of the Five Cangliu Masters]

7
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,480
Tianque.

8
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:51,400
Is it coming from Tianque?
[Master Lang - One of the Five Cangliu Masters]

9
00:02:56,550 --> 00:03:00,880
Master Peng, what do you think?

10
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:04,420
Quickly mobilize troops to take care of the calamity.
[Master Peng - One of the Five Cangliu Masters]

11
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,950
This time is different.

12
00:03:08,950 --> 00:03:12,940
We don't even know who our rivals are.

13
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:16,860
How would we fight? Kill all passersby from Tianque?

14
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:20,280
You must know that Taoyuan Province is Gao Shunzhao's territory.

15
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:23,270
It is not under our control. We cannot act rashly.

16
00:03:23,270 --> 00:03:25,340
Who does Gao Shunzhao think he is?

17
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:27,950
Do we have to be afraid of him?
[Master Luo - One of the Five Cangliu Masters]

18
00:03:28,730 --> 00:03:32,080
Even ant bites can cause pain.

19
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:34,790
In that case, according to Cangliu rules,
[Master Gu - One of the Five Cangliu Masters]

20
00:03:34,790 --> 00:03:37,270
let's have everyone express their thoughts.

21
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:38,750
All right.

22
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:43,190
Those who support the Cangliu rules to kill whoever goes deep into the Taoyuan Province

23
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:46,250
and pass through Tianque,

24
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:48,650
please show it.

25
00:04:17,370 --> 00:04:20,380
No matter who it is, I hope this person

26
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:22,460
can bring Kongsang and Yunhuang

27
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:24,530
hope.

28
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:22,140
Who's secretly helping me?

29
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:32,730
Thank you for lending a helping hand.

30
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:37,960
Bai Ying?

31
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:09,550
♫ Among the frosty clouds is the cold moon ♫

32
00:06:09,550 --> 00:06:13,050
♫ A strange light in the night ♫

33
00:06:13,050 --> 00:06:15,630
♫ In the dream, there is longing and fear ♫

34
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:16,800
It's me.

35
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,650
Thank you for helping me.

36
00:06:19,820 --> 00:06:23,320
♫ The layers of waves build up ♫

37
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:26,850
♫ Repeating the promise ♫

38
00:06:26,850 --> 00:06:33,870
♫ Yet they disappear in the end ♫

39
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:37,380
♫ We've met several times ♫

40
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:40,690
♫ Yet it is hard to mention our fated relationship from the past ♫

41
00:06:40,690 --> 00:06:47,790
♫ Sighing over the past that is as frivolous as smoke ♫

42
00:06:47,790 --> 00:06:50,650
♫ Split open the cocoon in my heart ♫

43
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:53,960
I thought I was dreaming.

44
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:56,030
Is it really you?

45
00:06:56,030 --> 00:07:00,910
♫ Never been discovered by anyone ♫

46
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:04,810
♫ Ask time to borrow a chapter ♫

47
00:07:04,810 --> 00:07:07,780
♫ The unforgettable memories ♫

48
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:12,410
Don't leave me all alone again.

49
00:07:12,410 --> 00:07:14,380
I missed you so much.

50
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:17,330
In the past one hundred years...

51
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:22,390
For a hundred years I have seen you repeatedly in my dreams.

52
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:25,790
Just like when we were at the Jing pagoda.

53
00:07:25,790 --> 00:07:27,800
You smile

54
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:30,910
as you walked step by step towards me.

55
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:34,260
But every time I reach out to you,

56
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,320
you would disappear.

57
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:46,070
Turns out that this dream, I've dreamed again and again

58
00:07:47,850 --> 00:07:50,500
is because you were still alive.

59
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:57,770
♫ When I want to return,
it will be time for my dream to come true ♫

60
00:07:57,770 --> 00:08:01,150
I never thought I would be able to see you again.

61
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,690
How did you live for the past one hundred years?

62
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:10,800
Were you well?

63
00:08:13,050 --> 00:08:15,660
You've changed so much.

64
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:18,480
But you haven't changed at all.

65
00:08:19,350 --> 00:08:22,270
You're still the same as when we were at the Jing pagoda.

66
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,560
One hundred years have already passed.

67
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:35,840
Everything has changed.

68
00:08:37,260 --> 00:08:40,270
A hundred years ago, when I jumped off the pagoda,

69
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:42,760
Bai Ying died.

70
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:48,270
What happened to you?

71
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,820
You...

72
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,860
Is the change you speak of

73
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:10,180
because of him?

74
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:17,150
Just pretend you never saw me.

75
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:20,440
Pretend everything was just a dream.

76
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:23,350
Now that the dream is over,

77
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:27,220
everything must return to its original place.

78
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:22,680
What is this ghostly place?

79
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:34,440
What a stinky, long-faced Ice Cube, leaving me in a place like this. So heartless.

80
00:12:31,430 --> 00:12:34,200
Such a pretty gemstone!

81
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:41,990
[Heavenly Ring]

82
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:58,980
W-What is this?

83
00:13:04,380 --> 00:13:07,230
Why can't I take it off?

84
00:13:08,830 --> 00:13:11,380
It's not a demon, is it?

85
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:16,370
I'm doomed. I-I'm being haunted by a demon!

86
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:17,680
I...

87
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,780
I shouldn't have been greedy for valuables.

88
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:22,370
Can you come off?

89
00:13:23,830 --> 00:13:26,460
Why is this thing so demonic?

90
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:30,860
I'm begging you. Come off, please come off!

91
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:33,950
As long as you can come off, I will do anything you ask! I'm begging you.

92
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:37,010
Will you really do anything?

93
00:13:37,010 --> 00:13:40,370
Who is it? Who is it?

94
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,840
Who is it?

95
00:13:44,090 --> 00:13:46,920
Hurry and come out. Come out!

96
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:59,450
So it's a little girl.

97
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:02,080
Hello.

98
00:14:03,650 --> 00:14:05,750
Help!

99
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:26,430
Hey!

100
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:29,090
Looking for me?

101
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:34,250
Are you a human or a ghost?

102
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:37,280
Maybe...

103
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,720
A ghost!

104
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:42,700
- Don't come closer!
- Hey, little girl.

105
00:14:42,700 --> 00:14:45,720
Do I really look that scary? It's not like I'll eat you.

106
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:48,770
Besides, you're wearing my ring and you want to run away.

107
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:55,200
This... I can't take it off!

108
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:59,300
Of course. Don't waste your energy. You won't be able to take it off.

109
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:13,090
Amazing.

110
00:15:16,910 --> 00:15:18,930
Dangerous!

111
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,870
Don't come closer!

112
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:30,500
- Little girl, stop yelling!
- Help!

113
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:32,680
- Help! Ghost!
- Calm down.

114
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,810
- Ghost! Someone!
- The more you yell, the faster this place will collapse! Stop yelling!

115
00:15:34,810 --> 00:15:36,820
- Calm down.
- Ghost! Someone come!

116
00:15:36,820 --> 00:15:40,290
- So noisy!
- Help!

117
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:49,100
Ghost Brother. Ghost Brother.

118
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:53,440
Hurry and come out, Immortal Brother.

119
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,450
Save me!

120
00:15:56,450 --> 00:15:58,270
Hurry and work your powers. Use your powers.

121
00:15:58,270 --> 00:15:59,930
Please save me. As long as you save me,

122
00:15:59,930 --> 00:16:01,820
I will do anything you ask of me.

123
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:05,710
Little girl, use my ring to run towards here and you'll get to safety.

124
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:07,490
- Really?
- Don't keep standing there.

125
00:16:07,490 --> 00:16:10,160
You called me an immortal yet you're not listening to my words?

126
00:16:11,190 --> 00:16:13,550
Hurry! I'm leaving now.

127
00:16:26,540 --> 00:16:31,130
High Priest, come and look at this Water Mirror. Why is it suddenly acting abnormally?

128
00:16:31,950 --> 00:16:33,290
It's the Heavenly Ring.
 [Lan Xia - Prince Lan] [Hong Yuan - Reigning Princess Chi] [Qing Yuan - Prince Qing]

129
00:16:33,290 --> 00:16:34,550
[Lan Xia - Prince Lan] [Hong Yuan - Reigning Princess Chi] [Qing Yuan - Prince Qing]

130
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:37,590
It's the Heavenly Ring! It's the Heavenly Ring!

131
00:16:37,590 --> 00:16:40,980
It's been a hundred years and there's finally a reaction!

132
00:16:42,690 --> 00:16:46,660
The Heavenly Ring is at Tianque Snow Mountain now. I ask Your Highness's

133
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:49,220
to go there immediately to look for it.

134
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:51,100
Yes.

135
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,750
You'll do anything I say, is that right?

136
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:16,470
No, no! I said nonsense in a moment of desperation just now.

137
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:19,030
Take the ring back.

138
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:21,490
Then take the ring off.

139
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:24,020
But I can't seem to take it off!

140
00:17:24,020 --> 00:17:28,740
Thus, it's ordained by the heavens. It's too late to regret it.

141
00:17:31,600 --> 00:17:34,890
Then you tell me, what do you want me to do?

142
00:17:34,890 --> 00:17:38,280
I want you to wear the ring,

143
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:40,470
and go to Taoyuan Province.

144
00:17:40,470 --> 00:17:42,510
Taoyuan Province?

145
00:17:43,560 --> 00:17:45,930
It sounds so familiar.

146
00:17:45,930 --> 00:17:49,570
It's the small town closest to Tianque Snow Mountain.

147
00:17:49,570 --> 00:17:53,580
If they know that the Heavenly Ring has appeared,

148
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:56,120
they will surely go there to receive me.

149
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:23,660
I can't go any farther. I'm so tired!

150
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:25,810
I'm going to sleep for a bit.

151
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:30,390
Hey, little girl, it's better for you to go down the mountain quickly.

152
00:18:30,390 --> 00:18:35,180
No, no. The village elders said we shouldn't travel at night.

153
00:19:02,190 --> 00:19:06,390
One of the four seals has broken.

154
00:19:06,390 --> 00:19:12,230
The Heavenly Ring has reappeared. Relay my order immediately.

155
00:19:12,230 --> 00:19:15,640
Kill those who pass through Tianque.

156
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:18,310
Yes, Lord Zhi Zhe.

157
00:19:28,890 --> 00:19:32,470
Zhi Zhe said that the calamity is coming from Tianque.

158
00:19:32,470 --> 00:19:34,520
One of the four seals has broken.

159
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:39,010
Please guard the rest of the seals and dispatch soldiers immediately to Tianque.

160
00:19:39,010 --> 00:19:42,070
Those who pass through Tianque must be killed.

161
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:45,620
We shall follow the teachings of Zhi Zhe.

162
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:53,720
Last time, Yu Huan fought with someone at Ruosong Hall

163
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:58,930
and was sent to Banbu City as punishment. It's been three months now, right?

164
00:19:58,930 --> 00:20:00,690
Yes.

165
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:05,760
It's time to let your younger brother come back.

166
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:07,810
Thank you very much, Master Peng.

167
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:12,320
I watched you both grow up.

168
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:17,690
You are my children. I cannot bear to truly punish him.

169
00:20:17,690 --> 00:20:21,890
If you didn't take us in back then,

170
00:20:21,890 --> 00:20:25,180
I fear we would have died in the mouth of jackals.

171
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:29,440
There's no need to mention that.

172
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:34,430
As long as you two remember, it's enough.

173
00:20:35,890 --> 00:20:42,590
By the way, Banbu City is the closest to Tianque.

174
00:20:45,230 --> 00:20:47,570
Are you saying

175
00:20:47,570 --> 00:20:51,500
to let Yu Huan kill those who pass through Tianque?

176
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:55,540
This is a good opportunity. If Yu Huan succeeds,

177
00:20:55,540 --> 00:20:59,280
Master Lang will be unstable in his position.

178
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:05,210
I understand. I will send someone to relay the message to Yu Huan.

179
00:21:05,210 --> 00:21:06,830
Yu Zhu,

180
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:12,520
how long have you been by Lord Zhi Zhe's side?

181
00:21:13,690 --> 00:21:17,600
- It has been fifteen years.
- The previous saintesses

182
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:20,620
were only by his side for ten years.

183
00:21:20,620 --> 00:21:23,220
Not a single day less or more.

184
00:21:23,220 --> 00:21:27,730
He acts strictly and cautiously. There have been no mistakes in the past hundred years.

185
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:31,650
Yet when you are the saintess,

186
00:21:31,650 --> 00:21:34,220
he is acting abnormally.

187
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:39,910
Why does he keep you and not let you go?

188
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,910
I have no idea.

189
00:21:50,260 --> 00:21:52,650
He trusts you.

190
00:21:56,030 --> 00:22:02,130
Master Peng, I dare not speculate what is on Lord Zhi Zhe's mind.

191
00:22:05,170 --> 00:22:09,790
Serve him well.

192
00:22:10,820 --> 00:22:12,660
Yes.

193
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:34,800
[Banbu City - Desert]

194
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:43,800
[Yu Huan - Cangliu General]

195
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:09,800
[Xiao - Previous Leader of the Quanxian Tribe]

196
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:13,200
Such meager skills yet you dare to attempt to assassinate me.

197
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:18,300
Yu Huan, Cangliu's dog. Everyone wants to kill you.

198
00:23:18,300 --> 00:23:21,800
Right now, it looks like you'll die first.

199
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:25,700
You might as well kill me right now.

200
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:30,600
Kill you? Isn't that going easy on you?

201
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:36,400
Answer my question.

202
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,700
Who was the other person who tried to assassinate me with you?

203
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:41,200
You won't get a word of information from my mouth.

204
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:45,000
We are 30 miles from Banbu City. I'm going to kill you by keeping you here.

205
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:48,000
If I die, you won't be able to leave here either.

206
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:51,400
From what I know,

207
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:54,900
once you are away from water for three days, you will dry up and die.

208
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:57,400
You haven't drunk water for a day now.

209
00:23:57,400 --> 00:24:00,000
If one of us dies, you will die before me.

210
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:04,590
Then I feel a bit regretful.

211
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:09,230
I can't personally see you waiting for death.

212
00:24:11,650 --> 00:24:13,410
You want to die?

213
00:24:15,900 --> 00:24:18,200
Not that easy!

214
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,700
Younger sister.

215
00:24:57,770 --> 00:24:59,370
Younger sister.

216
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:07,100
Drink this water.

217
00:25:12,100 --> 00:25:15,200
You spilled the last bit of the water.

218
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:49,800
I'm tired to death. So tired.

219
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:56,000
It's daytime again so quickly. Soon I have to get going.

220
00:25:57,200 --> 00:26:00,100
Heaven, I beg you to protect me.

221
00:26:00,100 --> 00:26:03,400
Please don't let me meet any more strange people.

222
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:16,000
You won't be able to take it off.

223
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:17,800
Why can't I take this worn ring off?

224
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:20,200
That is not some "worn" ring.

225
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:23,000
It's called the "Heavenly Ring."

226
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:25,600
I don't care if it's heavenly.

227
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:28,200
I really am just a common person from the Central Plains.

228
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:30,400
Immortal Brother, just let me go.

229
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:32,000
I don't have a choice either.

230
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:34,300
This ring is really stubborn.

231
00:26:34,300 --> 00:26:38,400
Once it recognizes someone as its master, no one can change that.

232
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:40,400
Unless...

233
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:44,900
Unless its next master appears.

234
00:26:44,900 --> 00:26:46,500
Then, what should I do?

235
00:26:46,500 --> 00:26:48,100
Didn't I say?

236
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:51,500
Wear it and go to Taoyuan Province.

237
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:55,600
- Really?
- Yes.

238
00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:00,600
Something's not right.

239
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:03,000
Who exactly are you?

240
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:06,600
- I'm an immortal.
- You're lying.

241
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,940
I...

242
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:14,600
am the last master of the ring.

243
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:16,780
Then, why doesn't it want you anymore?

244
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:20,600
It's a long story. If I have the chance in the future, I will tell you.

245
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:24,000
Since you're so powerful, why don't you take it there yourself?

246
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,200
I'm...

247
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:30,000
actually a knowledgeable spirit bound to the ring.

248
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:34,200
Only the person who can wear the ring can see me.

249
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:39,600
The real me is in a deep sleep.

250
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:43,200
Say, little girl, I'm giving you a chance to repay my kindness.

251
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:45,800
Besides, with that small body of yours,

252
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:50,100
it'll be very difficult for you to leave Tianque without my guidance.

253
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:53,800
All right. I'll do it.

254
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:57,000
I'll only take the ring there but I won't be responsible for anything else.

255
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:59,000
All right. Go on then.

256
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,000
Wait.

257
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:05,100
Do I get anything out of repaying your kindness?

258
00:28:05,100 --> 00:28:06,500
"Get anything?"

259
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:08,800
I didn't get anything beneficial for saving you yesterday!

260
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:11,300
Yet you're asking me for something.

261
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:16,600
Forget it. I'm a very benevolent person.

262
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:19,400
As long as you safely take the ring to Taoyuan Province,

263
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:21,000
I'll naturally give you something beneficial.

264
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,200
What is it?

265
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:24,300
What do you want?

266
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:27,700
I don't want much.

267
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:31,000
Just give me a bit of Yunhuang money.

268
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:33,000
A greedy person who doesn't care about her life.

269
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,600
All right then.

270
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:36,200
- Really?
- Of course.

271
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:39,400
That's great! That's great! Let's go now.

272
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:41,600
Wait.

273
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:46,000
Remember, don't let anyone see you wearing the Heavenly Ring.

274
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,400
All right, all right. Don't worry.

275
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:51,600
If you deceive a handsome man like me,

276
00:28:51,600 --> 00:28:53,800
I will have retribution.

277
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:59,600
By the way, your name is Na Sheng, right?

278
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:03,000
- How did you know?
- I'm an immortal.

279
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:09,000
Enough. Hurry and go.

280
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:13,200
Then I'll get going now. I'm going.

281
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:27,800
We've found the general!

282
00:29:37,100 --> 00:29:39,300
Where's that convict?
 [Banbu City - Military Camp]

283
00:29:39,300 --> 00:29:42,800
We gave her some water, and someone is watching over her.

284
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:45,600
Rest assured. You worked painstakingly hard to capture her.
[Fei Lian - Cangliu General]

285
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:47,800
Surely, you'll be the one to interrogate her.
[Fei Lian - Cangliu General]

286
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:53,400
But I'll have to trouble you. Help me send that convict back to Jing City.

287
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:57,200
Don't worry. We will wait for you to come back to conduct the interrogation.

288
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,600
I hid some good wine in the residence.

289
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:02,800
Then we won't stop drinking until we get drunk.

290
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:09,600
Report! A secret order from Jing City.

291
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:15,000
Master Peng has ordered you to rush to Tianque immediately

292
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:18,800
and kill those who pass through Tianque. This pearl has strong powers.

293
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:21,600
It could help you escape danger in time of crisis.

294
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:25,600
Only you and I know about this. Yu Zhu.

295
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:54,400
Immortal Brother? Immortal Brother?

296
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:57,600
Hey! Here!

297
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:00,560
- Who's there?
- Hide.

298
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:27,500
- Just now...
- There's no one. Did you hear wrong?

299
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:30,100
The higher-ups have ordered all those who pass through Tianque to be killed.

300
00:31:30,100 --> 00:31:32,200
No one can be spared.

301
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:35,700
Every year, there are so many who pass through Tianque. Do we kill them all?

302
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:37,700
I also heard there was an avalanche.

303
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:40,200
I'm guessing that those who were passing through have died in the avalanche.

304
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:42,000
Who could possibly be alive?

305
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,800
It's so cold. Let's go make a fire.

306
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,700
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

307
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,600
Come on out.

308
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:10,000
Immortal Brother, they won't kill me, will they?

309
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:14,000
Rest assured, I will warn you if there's any danger.

310
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:18,300
Even though I don't know if you are a human or a ghost,

311
00:32:18,300 --> 00:32:21,400
you seem to have some loyalty, unlike that stinky Ice Cube.

312
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,500
He left me all alone here on this snow mountain.

313
00:32:23,500 --> 00:32:25,100
Who's stinky Ice Cube?

314
00:32:25,100 --> 00:32:30,100
It's a person who is a bit good-looking but has a very, very bad temperament.

315
00:32:30,100 --> 00:32:34,300
Usually, those who are good-looking have bad temperaments.

316
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:38,000
No wonder your temperament is all right.

317
00:32:39,100 --> 00:32:41,800
I won't care about you either, you stinky girl.

318
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:47,800
Immortal Brother! Immortal Bother? Immortal Brother!

319
00:32:48,700 --> 00:32:50,800
You're good-looking!

320
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,800
Unbelievable.

321
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,800
Look at this.

322
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:05,000
I've never seen pearls so big.

323
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,000
Look at mine.

324
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:08,500
Is this the reason why you are failing to do your duties?

325
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:12,200
- General.
- General.

326
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:14,000
Have you encountered anyone passing through Tianque?

327
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:18,400
We have been guarding the entrance and didn't see anyone.

328
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:20,700
Drinking and roasting meat. Your eyes are full of money.

329
00:33:20,700 --> 00:33:22,700
How could you encounter anyone who is passing through Tianque?

330
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:23,800
General,

331
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:26,800
have mercy on us. We don't dare to act this way again.

332
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:28,400
Take them away.

333
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:31,400
- G-General! General!
- General!

334
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:33,000
- We don't dare act like this again.
- That's right.

335
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:34,600
- Have mercy of us, General!
- We know we were wrong.

336
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:37,000
Spare us, General!

337
00:34:15,310 --> 00:34:17,580
The sun will rise soon.

338
00:34:22,160 --> 00:34:25,370
I have to find a place to hide quickly.

