457
00:41:30,640 --> 00:41:32,590
Immortal Brother! Immortal Brother!

458
00:41:32,590 --> 00:41:34,670
Immortal Brother!

459
00:41:34,670 --> 00:41:36,430
Brother Ice Cube!

460
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:39,990
