464
00:41:47,980 --> 00:41:49,910
Take me to Taoyuan Province!

465
00:41:49,910 --> 00:41:51,520
Why?

466
00:41:54,070 --> 00:41:55,760
Look.

467
00:42:01,790 --> 00:42:03,510
Heavenly Ring?

468
00:42:12,840 --> 00:42:15,000
